      <title>由于数据冲击恢复问题，中国股市暴跌加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-stocks-slump-as-concerns-mount-on-disappointing-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列令人失望的经济数据加剧了市场的看跌情绪，周三中国股市的跌势进一步加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-stocks-slump-as-concerns-mount-on-disappointing-data</guid>
